dataValues.values: Mitie operates many internal and external websites providing services to the business.  These websites are hosted on an IIS web farm that is highly available.  Four servers are hosted in two separate datacentres (two in each) and web content and configurations are synchronised across the web servers using DFS.  This is achieved by each webserver being a domain member of the MITIEGRP domain.
Business Priority is Low as per CBIS. For Prod, application tier as Platinum and for QA, its mentioned as Bronze. As per Master Reference, For PROD its mentioned as GOLD. Need clarification
Many mission critical websites are hosted on the IIS web farm.

Mitie is managing IIS and Vodafone will patch the servers
